Achievements.Name: Till All Are One
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Supreme Commander
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty using Optimus Prime.

Achievements.Name: Sting Like a Bee
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty using Bumblebee.

Achievements.Name: The Wizard of Iacon
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty using Wheeljack.

Achievements.Name: Raging Bull
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty using Sideswipe.

Achievements.Name: The King
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters on any difficulty using Grimlock.

Achievements.Name: All Clear
Achievements.Description: Complete all Challenge Mode missions on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Halfway There
Achievements.Description: Complete half of all Challenge Mode missions on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: No Stone Unturned
Achievements.Description: Collect all collectible items.

Achievements.Name: Avid Collector
Achievements.Description: Collect half of all collectible items.

Achievements.Name: Synthesis 101
Achievements.Description: Synthesize 10 weapons.

Achievements.Name: Full Throttle
Achievements.Description: Defeat 100 enemies with Vehicle/Dino Attacks.

Achievements.Name: (Don't) Hit the Brakes!
Achievements.Description: Defeat 100 enemies with Rush Attacks.

Achievements.Name: Platinum
Achievements.Description: Complete all chapters, earning the highest rank, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater.

Achievements.Name: Catch this!
Achievements.Description: Use parrying to catch the following from an enemy: a boulder, a missile, and both drill types.

Achievements.Name: Pedal to the Metal
Achievements.Description: Use Focus 100 times.

Achievements.Name: Quick Reflexes
Achievements.Description: After dodging, quickly counter with a melee attack 100 times.

Achievements.Name: Bullet Storm
Achievements.Description: After dodging, quickly counter with a ranged attack 100 times.

Achievements.Name: Hawkeyed
Achievements.Description: Perform 100 successful head shots.

Achievements.Name: Flyswatter
Achievements.Description: Finish the lift battle in Chapter 2 without taking damage from Insecticons.

Achievements.Name: Urban Landscaping
Achievements.Description: In chapter 1, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, knock Devastator into a building 3 times.

Achievements.Name: Roadblock
Achievements.Description: In chapter 4, defeat Motormaster while racing him.

Achievements.Name: Surround Sound
Achievements.Description: In chapter 6, on diff. COMMANDER or greater, defeat Soundwave without defeating any cassettes.

Achievements.Name: Wrecking Crew
Achievements.Description: In chapter 1, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Devastator without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: HARD-Core
Achievements.Description: In chapter 2, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, destroy the shielding without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Triple Changer
Achievements.Description: In chapter 3, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Blitzwing without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Destruction Derby
Achievements.Description: In chapter 4, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Menasor without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Don't Look Him in the Eye
Achievements.Description: In chapter 5, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Shockwave without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Broken Radio
Achievements.Description: In chapter 6, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Soundwave without taking damage.

Achievements.Name: Emperor of Destruction
Achievements.Description: In chapter 7, on difficulty COMMANDER or greater, defeat Megatron without taking damage.
